WEBVTT


01:12:28.385 --> 01:12:31.305 line:85.83%,end
<i>I sent him a message
that his sister will die if he doesn't</i>

01:12:31.388 --> 01:12:33.432 line:85.83%,end
<i>blow himself up
with the hostages by midnight.</i>

01:12:33.515 --> 01:12:35.267 line:85.83%,end
So trust me and be patient.

01:12:35.351 --> 01:12:37.019 line:85.83%,end
<i>That's great!</i>

01:12:37.102 --> 01:12:39.104 line:85.83%,end
Them blowing themselves up?
That's way better.

01:12:39.188 --> 01:12:41.732 line:14.17%,start
<i>What if Kang makes off
with 300 million dollars?</i>

01:12:41.815 --> 01:12:43.942 line:14.17%,start
<i>Just trust her and wait for her?</i>

01:12:44.026 --> 01:12:45.444 line:14.17%,start
<i>Once she has that much money,</i>

01:12:45.527 --> 01:12:47.529 line:14.17%,start
<i>she might flee to another country.</i>

01:12:49.365 --> 01:12:51.867 line:14.17%,start
<i>I'll help you
get only Yeong-ro out of here.</i>

01:12:55.287 --> 01:12:57.998 line:14.17%,start
Your father is the ANSP director?

01:12:58.082 --> 01:13:00.501 line:14.17%,start
<i>Isn't he the one trying to kill us all?</i>

01:13:00.584 --> 01:13:02.544 line:14.17%,start
<i>Yeong-ro's such a murderer's daughter?</i>

01:13:02.628 --> 01:13:04.505 line:14.17%,start
<i>That's so creepy!</i>

01:13:04.588 --> 01:13:07.674 line:14.17%,start
I want to help you get out alive.

01:13:07.758 --> 01:13:10.469 line:14.17%,start
<i>I'll get in the same car as Soo-ho.</i>

01:13:11.095 --> 01:13:12.513 line:14.17%,start
<i>I'm sorry I've put you</i>

01:13:13.847 --> 01:13:15.099 line:14.17%,start
<i>through all this.</i>

01:13:16.725 --> 01:13:17.976 line:14.17%,start
<i>Soo-ho.</i>

01:13:18.602 --> 01:13:21.605 line:85.83%,end
I'll stay by your side until the end.

01:13:25.651 --> 01:13:28.445 line:85.83%,end
BONUS

01:13:31.365 --> 01:13:35.994 line:85.83%,end
You're Linda Young, a fund manager
at ABK Partners based in Hong Kong.

01:13:36.537 --> 01:13:38.664 line:85.83%,end
And you're flying to the New York HQ
tomorrow morning

01:13:38.747 --> 01:13:40.541 line:85.83%,end
to have a conference meeting.

01:13:40.624 --> 01:13:42.793 line:85.83%,end
I'm Gong Gil-sun,

01:13:42.876 --> 01:13:45.879 line:85.83%,end
who used to scam US soldiers in Osaka.

01:13:45.963 --> 01:13:48.924 line:85.83%,end
I'm the Gong Gil-sun.
Don't you know my nickname?

01:13:49.007 --> 01:13:51.343 line:85.83%,end
Of course I do. "Threatening Gong."

01:13:54.096 --> 01:13:56.098 line:85.83%,end
